HEADWORD: Proface
<hw>Pro"face</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>prou
face</ets>, <ets>prou fasse</ets>; <ets>prou</ets> profit +
<ets>faire</ets> to make, do.]</ety> <def>Much good may it do you! -- a
familiar salutation or welcome.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Master page, good master page, sit. <qex>Proface</qex>!</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Profanate</ent>⟦br⟧
